# 📝 Task 2 - Simple To-Do List App

This is a simple **command-line To-Do List application** built with **Node.js** as part of my internship tasks. It allows users to **add**, **view**, and **delete** tasks from the list directly in the terminal.

---

## 🚀 Features
- ✅ Add new tasks  
- 📋 View all tasks  
- 🗑️ Delete tasks by number  
- Beginner-friendly implementation  

---

